OL,5,BBlocktober 2020              Q l+f?2   
OL,7,BPhysical gatherings are still prevented
OL,8,Bby an ongoing global pandemic, so we've
OL,9,Bdecided to do another online blockparty
OL,10,Blike April'sEBlockdown 2020.           
OL,12,BThe editing server will be open to the 
OL,13,Binternet for remote editing again, and 
OL,14,Beverything will be streamed live at    
OL,15,Etwitch.tv/zxguesser.                   
OL,17,BJoin us on the teletext discord server 
OL,18,BatEdiscord.gg/f7eWb73.                 
